snippet.title: Winter Survival – 25 Minutes of Demo Gameplay
snippet.description:
Check out the demo now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1394960/Winter_Survival/

Survivors! The day has finally come – our brand-new demo is already available. Check this 25 minutes of gameplay if you want to learn more about the demo and our game - coming to Early Access on February 28th, 2024.
